reveal-sc2-opponent-main/data/config.json.pre-*

# Transient broken/migration backups (production snapshots are kept by the backup router)
**/MyOpponentHistory.json.broken-*
**/MyOpponentHistory.json.bom-*
reveal-sc2-opponent-main/data/meta_database.json.broken-*
reveal-sc2-opponent-main/data/meta_database.json.pre-chrono-fix-*
reveal-sc2-opponent-main/data/meta_database.json.pre-chain-counting-*
